{"id":"meshtastic-captains-compass-31d","title":"v0.2 BEAD-11: CompassUI","description":"firmware-overlay/src/modules/CompassModule/CompassUI.{h,cpp} per TDD section 14. wantUIFrame(), interceptingKeyboardInput(), drawFrame(), handleInputEvent(). Arrow geometry tip(0,-18)/wings(±9,-4)/tail(0,12) rotated by headingError using sinf/cosf (nRF52840 FPU). Blinks at 500ms when signal lost \u003e90s. Screens: DISCOVERING node list, TRACKING compass, PAIR_INCOMING accept/reject, CALIBRATING sample counter, TRACKING_TREASURE with YOU'RE HERE at \u003c15m. Long-press 800ms threshold. Acceptance: arrow tip up at heading error 0; rotates correctly at +/-45/90/180; blinks on signal lost; PAIR_INCOMING ACCEPT calls sendPairAccept; CALIBRATING sample count increments; TRACKING long-press releases UI frame; YOU'RE HERE at \u003c15m. Depends on BEAD-8/9/10.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","owner":"nathanjbarlow@gmail.com","created_at":"2026-05-02T06:05:10Z","created_by":"Nathan Barlow","updated_at":"2026-05-02T07:08:10Z","closed_at":"2026-05-02T07:08:10Z","close_reason":"CompassUI complete. firmware-overlay/src/modules/CompassModule/CompassUI.{h,cpp} written for 240x135 ST7789 TFT (drawing primitives via OLEDDisplay abstraction). wantUIFrame/interceptingKeyboardInput active in DISCOVERING/AWAITING_PAIR_ACCEPT/PAIR_INCOMING/TRACKING/SESSION_PAUSED/TRACKING_TREASURE/CALIBRATING. Arrow geometry: tip(0,-40)/wings(±20,-10)/tail(0,25), rotated by sinf/cosf (nRF52840 FPU). Blink at 500ms when isSignalLost(). YOU'RE HERE replaces arrow at distance \u003c 15m for treasures. Full per-state renderers + per-state input handling. Long-press SELECT or BACK releases UI in TRACKING. CompassModule.h adds Observable\u003cUIFrameEvent*\u003e, drawFrame override, CallbackObserver for InputBroker. Compiles cross-arch. Hardware verification deferred.","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"meshtastic-captains-compass-31d","depends_on_id":"meshtastic-captains-compass-1hx","type":"blocks","create