{"id":"meshtastic-captains-compass-uwv","title":"v0.2 BEAD-10: CompassModule","description":"firmware-overlay/src/modules/CompassModule/CompassModule.{h,cpp} per TDD section 13. Extends SinglePortModule (COMPASS_APP port) and OSThread. handleReceived() dispatches all 8 CompassMsgType values; runOnce() drives TRACKED position updates and TRACKING timeout detection; send helpers (sendCapabilityQuery, sendPairRequest, sendPairAccept, sendPairReject, sendSessionEnd). Static instance pointer. Acceptance: make build succeeds; module registers on COMPASS_APP port (other ports ignored); sendCapabilityQuery() emits broadcast hop_limit=0; injected mock PAIR_REQUEST → PAIR_INCOMING; TRACKED runOnce sends at configured interval; wantUIFrame() correct per state. Depends on BEAD-6/7/9.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"Nathan Barlow","owner":"nathanjbarlow@gmail.com","created_at":"2026-05-02T06:04:53Z","created_by":"Nathan Barlow","updated_at":"2026-05-02T07:07:59Z","closed_at":"2026-05-02T07:07:59Z","close_reason":"CompassModule complete. firmware-overlay/src/modules/CompassModule/CompassModule.{h,cpp} written. Extends SinglePortModule(meshtastic_PortNum_COMPASS_APP) + Observable\u003cUIFrameEvent*\u003e + concurrency::OSThread. handleReceived() decodes via pb_decode_from_bytes and dispatches all 8 CompassMsgType values to per-message handlers. send helpers use allocDataPacket + pb_encode_to_bytes + service-\u003esendToMesh(RX_SRC_LOCAL). Hop limits: 0 for discovery/pair handshake, 3 for POSITION_UPDATE/SESSION_END. Auto-responds to CAPABILITY_QUERY regardless of UI state. tickTracked() pulls localPosition + powerStatus-\u003egetBatteryChargePercent() and sends per-interval position updates. Static instance pointer set in ctor. Compiles cross-arch but not yet linked into binary (BEAD-12 wires it via Modules.cpp patch).","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"meshtastic-captains-compass-uwv","depends_on_id":"meshtastic-captains-compass-2hg","type":"blocks","cr