{"id":"meshtastic-captains-compass-sm8","title":"v0.2 BEAD-9: CompassState","description":"firmware-overlay/src/modules/CompassModule/CompassState.{h,cpp} per TDD section 12. 9-state FSM (IDLE/DISCOVERING/AWAITING_PAIR_ACCEPT/PAIR_INCOMING/TRACKING/TRACKED/TRACKING_TREASURE/SESSION_PAUSED/CALIBRATING). NVS namespace 'compass'. Treasure CRUD (max 5), calibration sample accumulation (min 50), Desire-side update suppression (5min stationary keepalive). Acceptance: make build succeeds; state transitions match diagram; saveTreasure/treasure round-trip through NVS across reboot; shouldSendUpdate suppression behavior correct; finishCalibration() returns false if \u003cMIN_CAL_SAMPLES; cal-version mismatch returns zero offsets, no crash. Depends on BEAD-8.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"Nathan Barlow","owner":"nathanjbarlow@gmail.com","created_at":"2026-05-02T06:04:49Z","created_by":"Nathan Barlow","updated_at":"2026-05-02T07:00:22Z","closed_at":"2026-05-02T07:00:22Z","close_reason":"CompassState complete. firmware-overlay/src/modules/CompassModule/CompassState.{h,cpp} written. Full 9-state FSM (IDLE/DISCOVERING/AWAITING_PAIR_ACCEPT/PAIR_INCOMING/TRACKING/TRACKED/TRACKING_TREASURE/SESSION_PAUSED/CALIBRATING). Persistence via FSCom (cross-arch — InternalFS on nRF52, LittleFS elsewhere) at /compass/cal /compass/treasures /compass/settings, all versioned binary structs that ignore mismatched schema. Treasure CRUD up to 5 entries, calibration sample accumulation with min 50 samples, hard-iron offsets via min/max midpoint per axis. Desire-side update suppression: send if first-time OR distance \u003e 5m floor OR 5min keepalive elapsed. Compiles cross-arch. NVS round-trip + FSM transition validation deferred to hardware testing.","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"meshtastic-captains-compass-sm8","depends_on_id":"meshtastic-captains-compass-1hx","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-05-02T01:05:30Z","created_by":"Nathan Barlow","metadata":"{}"}],"dependenc