{"id":"meshtastic-captains-compass-3up","title":"v0.2 BEAD-5: Variant patch (variant.h + variant.cpp)","description":"Read vendor/meshtastic-firmware/variants/nrf52840/heltec_mesh_node_t114/variant.h and variant.cpp. Choose stable anchor in variant.h, implement patch_variant_h injecting MAG_SDA/MAG_SCL/WIRE_INTERFACES_COUNT/WIRE1_INTERFACES_COUNT/PIN_WIRE1_SDA/PIN_WIRE1_SCL defines per TDD section 8. Verify whether BSP auto-creates Wire1 from PIN_WIRE1_* defines by inspecting other nRF52 variants with WIRE_INTERFACES_COUNT=2; if manual instantiation needed, implement patch_variant_cpp adding TwoWire Wire1(NRF_TWIM1, ...). Acceptance: make build succeeds; on real T114 with QMC5883L wired, Wire1.beginTransmission(0x0D) returns ACK. Depends on BEAD-3.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"Nathan Barlow","owner":"nathanjbarlow@gmail.com","created_at":"2026-05-02T06:04:22Z","created_by":"Nathan Barlow","updated_at":"2026-05-02T06:43:43Z","closed_at":"2026-05-02T06:43:43Z","close_reason":"No variant patch required. Upstream T114 variant.h already defines WIRE_INTERFACES_COUNT=2 + PIN_WIRE1_SDA=P0.16 + PIN_WIRE1_SCL=P0.13. Verified that no nRF52 variant in upstream explicitly instantiates Wire1 in variant.cpp; BSP auto-creates it from PIN_WIRE1_* macros at static init. patch_variant_h and patch_variant_cpp kept as documented no-ops in apply.py for clarity. PRD pin assignment (was reversed) updated to match upstream. make build still succeeds. Hardware ACK verification deferred to BEAD-7.","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"meshtastic-captains-compass-3up","depends_on_id":"meshtastic-captains-compass-yun","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-05-02T01:05:27Z","created_by":"Nathan Barlow","metadata":"{}"}],"dependency_count":1,"dependent_count":1,"comment_count":0}
